<div style="text-align: justify;">
<p>Came here from the YouTube reading to tell that I enjoy this tale very much.</p>
<p>The part I find most interesting is the idea that 343, 2343 and his wife are all manifestation of the same being.</p>
<p>Also, putting two scips together draws attention to their articles in a way - and it is hard not to notice how the wiki has evolved. God of series I basically is not contained, while God in series III IS and his containment has redundancies and stuff even though the reader doesn't even see his powers to the extent of 343.</p>
</div>

